creator: 时代的迷失香
descriptionHtml:
Easily set TikTok video as mobile desktop wallpaper, personalize your mobile phone.

Here are the most popular short video resources on TikTok. You can setting it as wallpaper, and you can also download the video to your mobile locally.

Functions:

1. Can set video wallpaper with or without sound

2. Screen Display Mode of Video Wallpaper

3. Video wallpaper can be set to double-click desktop pause

4. add the Functions of Video Albums

5. download titok Videos
descriptionShort: TikTok video wallpapers are easy to set up

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: 1.Fix a bug that crashes when setting wallpaper on a few phones
